India's Imports of South African Coal Fell 40% in March From Year Earlier

-- B y   D i n a k a r   S e t h u r a m a n
-- 
2011-04-11T06:16:04Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-11/india-s-imports-of-south-african-coal-fell-40-in-march-from-year-earlier.html
India ’s imports of coal from  South
Africa  dropped 40 percent in March from a year earlier to 1.48
million metric tons, according to data from mjunction Services
Ltd.  China ’s imports from South Africa rose 13 percent to
451,391 tons, the Kolkata-based trader said in an e-mail.  To contact the reporter on this story:
